Package: jmed
Type: Package
Title: Mediation Analysis with Joint Models of Longitudinal and Time-to-Event Data
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Lina Kramer 
Maintainer: Lina Kramer <linakramer015@gmail.com>
Description: This package can be used for mediation analysis. jm_mediate() 
    computes total, direct, and indirect effects over time from a joint model 
    object (fit in JMbayes2). The function implements a g-computation approach, 
    broadly following Zheng & Liu (2021).
Imports: 
  JMbayes2,
  MASS,
  statmod
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
